page.title: 17BIOGRAPHY CONTINUED
page.content: ALISON WAS BORN IN THE VILLAGE AND IS ENGAGED TO A FARMERS SON LOCALLY SO SHE WILL CONTINUE TO LIVE IN THE AREA AFTER SHE MARRIES. SHE HAS NO REGRETS ABOUT THIS AS SHE CONSIDERS LIVING IN THE AREA A VERY HAPPY LIFE. HER INTERESTS INCLUDE PLAYING POOL KEEPING FIT HORSERIDING DANCING AND TENNIS. SHE SAYS THAT HOLBEACH DROVE ITSELF CONSISTS OF MAINLY BOYS SO ONE HAS TO LEAD A BIT OF A BOYS LIFESTYLE BUT I AM SURE THE BOYS DO NOT THINKS OF HER LIKE THAT! SHE HAS A DOG PATCH AND A CAT BALLS AND A RABBIT ROSCO. WHEN WINNING THE TITLE WHICH HER OFFICE PUT HER FORWARD FOR SHE RECEIVED A SASH AND A SILVER ROSEBOWL ALSO A CHEQUE FOR FIVE HUNDRED POUNDS WHICH IS TO INCLUDE A DRESS ALLOWANCE FOR THE MANY FUNCTIONS SHE WILL ATTEND.
